{"tid":1121584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州話係正宗?","createTime":"2019-04-23T11:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:21:54.000Z","uid":142242,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"87e07851e6edce5590e293359eaa86154a7a7d7b","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"其實係唔係唔知粵語都有唔同子方言，所有語言都會因地域區隔、人口流動而演變成不同子方言，粵語都唔例外。<br />\n<br />\n成日話廣州正宗，根本係偽議題，純粹因為廣州係省城，有社經地位，加上香港歌影視發展，先至令廣州腔成為粵語最強勢嘅腔調。孫中山段粵語錄音都係石岐話，唔通又話佢粵語唔正宗?圍村人啲圍頭話係莞寶片粵語，唔通又話佢地粵語唔正宗?<br />\n<br />\n廣東廣西咁大，有好多粵語分支同香港、廣州粵語有好大差異，所謂「十里不同音」，各地有自己特色。如果用自己腔調去論斷人地，咁係唔係反而我地做咗加害者，同用普通話滅方言班仆街有咩分別? 聽閒有粵西、廣西地區嘅人唔願講佢地嘅粵語，原因係驚自己口音畀珠三角一帶，講廣州話嘅人笑，咁係唔係代表我地被打壓嘅「粵語」同時都打壓緊其他語言? <br />\n<br />\n語言根本就係百花齊放，多元先至係語言美麗之處。因此，爭論何者為正宗，無甚意義。努力傳承本地語言，先至對得住自己嘅文化。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed7aa9448c5f3eb1db3ad648fda31dcb7d71caa","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":108,"score":-105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"廣東話只係方言，毫無語言美感"},{"pid":"b73a535b069e8f7485c87b3f3efe15f75b075669","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"4ed7aa9448c5f3eb1db3ad648fda31dcb7d71caa","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":108,"score":-105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"廣東話只係方言，毫無語言美感"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"如果話廣東話係漢語系方言，都無錯嘅。<br />\n美感呢家嘢，都係見仁見智。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係想講句屌你老母"},{"pid":"881a0a2bd41db8d5a6fd9507219e35b8aaf9c756","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":57,"score":-57,"quote":{"pid":"b73a535b069e8f7485c87b3f3efe15f75b075669","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"4ed7aa9448c5f3eb1db3ad648fda31dcb7d71caa","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":108,"score":-105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"廣東話只係方言，毫無語言美感"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"如果話廣東話係漢語系方言，都無錯嘅。<br />\n美感呢家嘢，都係見仁見智。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係想講句屌你老母"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"普通話吊打"},{"pid":"ef43d43d634ac3943392fb7b3e5a6b59d1a5740b","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"881a0a2bd41db8d5a6fd9507219e35b8aaf9c756","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":57,"score":-57,"quote":{"pid":"b73a535b069e8f7485c87b3f3efe15f75b075669","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"4ed7aa9448c5f3eb1db3ad648fda31dcb7d71caa","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":108,"score":-105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"廣東話只係方言，毫無語言美感"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"如果話廣東話係漢語系方言，都無錯嘅。<br />\n美感呢家嘢，都係見仁見智。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係想講句屌你老母"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:57:13.000Z","msg":"普通話吊打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40dd2c00996f1255800eeb64348f29dd0003af9f","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":50,"score":-50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"Btw 廣東話係普通話嘅分支<br />\n<br />\n即係等同香港係中國嘅附庸"},{"pid":"380c124aefbc2d9cd979e1a872776dd54aa0fb1a","tid":1121584,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"黃師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d81218cf09be5f480b81934cd5236daeeaf395","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"支持粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee0e2ccd6fbc88359be0f097f7fb7e3e9bc2425","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"40dd2c00996f1255800eeb64348f29dd0003af9f","tid":1121584,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":50,"score":-50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"Btw 廣東話係普通話嘅分支<br />\n<br />\n即係等同香港係中國嘅附庸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9"},{"pid":"8da4442dc2255955ba977260ed539d822c548723","tid":1121584,"uid":54929,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:05:26.000Z","msg":"條友一早block咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fb4b7a0941ff27bfab71469f15f655c2be437f","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2c8758bdcac1f47c9c317d5c44820407316d0f","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e348e57c6a622adbc38507b66dea15af729ba3f1","tid":1121584,"uid":25952,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"根本無咩正宗唔正宗<br />\n個乜野神駒話廣州話先係正宗 真係笑大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n語言/方言向來都根據地區 文化不同而變遷<br />\n不同語言/方言亦會互相影響<br />\n<br />\nBtw 廣東話係咪方語從來都基於政治因素同政治決定<br />\n廣東話根本有資格成為語言<br />\n樓上條柒頭收一收皮"},{"pid":"663be33c98ead43b1cd261a89ea330d5b8ea40d8","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e348e57c6a622adbc38507b66dea15af729ba3f1","tid":1121584,"uid":25952,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"根本無咩正宗唔正宗<br />\n個乜野神駒話廣州話先係正宗 真係笑大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n語言/方言向來都根據地區 文化不同而變遷<br />\n不同語言/方言亦會互相影響<br />\n<br />\nBtw 廣東話係咪方語從來都基於政治因素同政治決定<br />\n廣東話根本有資格成為語言<br />\n樓上條柒頭收一收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n<br />\n唔同語言可以係一個大語言/語系嘅子方言，但佢本身都一個語言<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，假如100年後，荃灣嘅廣東話自行演變，同香港主流廣東話有差異，咁「荃灣話」係香港廣東話嘅方言，但「荃灣話」本身都係一門語言"},{"pid":"923c7223e5fe7ecf4d1325417eed212d1dea928e","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b6c96176303369e86607f3b256ae972b5e11ae","tid":1121584,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"捍衛本土文化係應該<br />\n但踩低其他人嘅文化根本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff53cc0a63c9740bf875906962f8d0236880d56","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a832201a256bca481b96ce4c45da6a5edee270","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9424ff80085ac6e616dbd157c1cb6e85e1fcca06","tid":1121584,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"樓主做乜鳩自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0ab9116363c42f5f200524a3ce814aa4b6d547","tid":1121584,"uid":201926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"廣州話係咪正宗我唔知，知道普通話唔係正宗就得喇"},{"pid":"ad3c06340270fc8334e83efa5ef70f3e9611dd31","tid":1121584,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T18:10:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61a9fdc2e1155dc387d1cc8a086db276eb76e36b","tid":1121584,"uid":142242,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ad3c06340270fc8334e83efa5ef70f3e9611dd31","tid":1121584,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"de0ab9116363c42f5f200524a3ce814aa4b6d547","tid":1121584,"uid":201926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"s